        "meta_description": "The sweet impish girl who stalked the reluctant Auro (Amitabh Bachchan) all over the school campus in Paa (2009) is no more. Taruni Sachdev’s death in an air crash in Nepal recently has shocked filmmakers.",
        "meta_lang": "en",
